title: Missing Hexakill
body: I cannot join hexakill - image is from a few moments before i send this post

replies.body:
Hey LilBlue - 

Looks like you're in NA. The queue for Hexakill usually turns on in each region in the afternoon. For NA, it's around 12 PST.
It doesn't go up until this evening. Exactly when depends on your time zone.
